T(n)\le cn
T\left(\frac{n}2\right)\le cn\tag{1}
T(n)\le c\left(\frac{n}2\right)+c\left(\frac{n}2\right)+1=cn+1\;.
\log n
T(k)\leq c*k
O(n)
T(k)=ck-b
c,b>0
b\geq \frac{1}{2},c>0
T(n)=2T(\frac{n}{2})+1
T(n)=2T(\frac{n} {2} )+1\leq 2(c \frac{n}{2})+1=cn+1\ne cn
T(n)=2T(\frac{n} {2} )+1\leq 2(c\frac{n}{2}-b)+1=cn-(2b-1)\leq cn
